    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-08-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-08-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="33"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d33">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 863.0011/17.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <p>Great and Good Friend: Bowed down and with deeply afflicted heart, I inform you
                    that my dearly beloved nephew, His Serene, Imperial and Royal Highness, Archduke
                    Franz Ferdinand of Austria-Este, in the midst of the earnest performance of his
                    duty, together with his nobleminded wife, Her Highness the Duchess of Hohenberg,
                    who in the hour of danger remained faithfully by his side, on June 28 of this
                    year at Sarajevo, fell as victims of a horrible crime.</p>
                <p>With the friendly interest that you take in all the happenings concerning me and
                    my House, I cherish the assured hope that you will also take a sympathetic
                    interest in the above information and thereby lessen in some measure my grief
                    over this loss, which has touched me so severely.</p>
                <pb facs="0142" n="26" xml:id="pg_26"/>
                <p>I take advantage of this sorrowful occasion for the renewed assurance of my
                    highest esteem.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Franz Joseph</hi>
                    </signed>. <lb/>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vienna</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-08-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 2, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
